  "seed_text": "RCMP File 2026-9000-4785-6 relates to immigration fraud by Hongzhi Du, CICC license R709646. The subject collected $123,310 CAD from a client for provincial nomination services under the RRS program. Funds were deposited to a personal account rather than a trust account, violating CICC regulations. AIP endorsement documents provided were later confirmed as forgeries by the AIP program office."
